         table had no org_id column and the advisor's SearchRequest carried no
         FilterExpression, so cache hits crossed tenants. This changeset DELETEs
         existing rows (irrecoverable provenance + PII content) and adds a JSONB
         btree index on metadata->>'org_id' for the org-scoped FilterExpression
         the companion VectorStoreCacheAdvisor change introduces.
         See .claude/reports/audit-advisor-chain-2026-05-04.md F11/F17. -->
